OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWatchdog urges tougher line
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fon Covid test firms        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government needs to apply tougher  
OL,6, standards to its list of approved Covid
OL,7, travel test providers, the competition 
OL,8, watchdog has said.                     
OL,10,FThe call comes as part of fresh advice 
OL,11,Ffrom the Competition and Markets       
OL,12,FAuthority (CMA) amid concerns that     
OL,13,Fconsumers are being ripped off.        
OL,15,FUK travellers must take PCR tests when 
OL,16,Fthey return from abroad, choosing from 
OL,17,Fa list of 400 or more authorised firms.
OL,19,FBut the CMA said basic standards should
OL,20,Fbe upgraded and enforced.              
